text: RT @monkeydom: I spent the first decade of my serious computer life with Acorn. The Archimedes, RiscOS and later the RiscPC spoiled me for life. Hard to put in words how far ahead of the time they were. Sadly a lack of style and marketing ended Acorn way ahead of time. https://t.co/zuh2Vefylz
